name: vestige_012: a message from the Dead God?
description: [partial decryption start]--- on my phone... it's starting to make me feel a little uncomfortable though. KBREWER: Oh GOD tell me you haven't been trying to read it!? DO NOT READ IT! CCHOI: oh no. oh SHIT Kristen what do you think I've been doing for the last 30 minutes! I thought it was some kind of joke from the synchronicity department! KBREWER: Okay this is fine, this is okay. I've ordered a decon protocol for you. Stay where you are. Do not read any more. Put your phone down. Take the battery out. Throw it out the window. CCHOI: you know it's strange, now that you mention it, it really does seem like there is some legible text in there... ---[partial decryption end]
